---
title: Pork Meatballs & Thai Red Curry Coconut Sauce with Asian Slaw & Crushed Peanuts
description: On first look, this may seem like just meatballs and slaw, but let’s dig a little deeper. You might notice the flavoursome red sauce
coating the meatballs, that’s in fact a coconutty Thai red curry sauce. Wrapping up this investigation are the peanuts sprinkled
invitingly in the slaw. This dinner is delicious, case closed!

*This recipe is under 650kcal per serving and under 30g carbohydrates per serving.*
